      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for a dependable daily driver that won't let you down? This vehicle is in fair condition and is ready to get you where you need to go! While it shows some expected wear and tear from its time on the road, it remains a solid, functional choice for anyone seeking reliable transportation at a great value. It's a practical option with plenty of character and many more miles to give!",
