    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would make a reliable daily driver for someone who doesn't mind some cosmetic imperfections. The exterior shows its age with several noticeable scratches, a few small door dings, and some fading on the clear coat on the roof. Inside, the upholstery has some minor staining and visible wear on the driver's seat bolster. Mechanically, the car starts and runs, though the suspension is starting to feel a bit loose and it will likely need new tires and a brake service within the next few months. It's an honest car that reflects its mileage and age accurately.",
